      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AVA'S PRIDE (1) has been out of the placings the last couple but was a Maiden winner (23.11) three back at Shepparton. This looks easier and expected to bounce back. MAD MAX (7) is having his first start around this course. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 2.75 lengths (17.29) at Healesville. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Can do much better this time. CRUISING AMY (8) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (17.40) at Healesville behind Why Not Hayden in a Bottom Up - Grade 6. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Can measure up. JUMBUK JADE (5) will run well despite no experience on this track.",
